Package: Nestimate
Title: Network Estimation, Bootstrap, and Higher-Order Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", email = "saqr@saqr.me", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Sonsoles", "López-Pernas", email = "sonsoles.lopez@uef.fi", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Estimate networks from sequence and panel data. Supports transition
    networks (relative, frequency, co-occurrence), association networks
    (correlation, partial correlation, graphical lasso, Ising), bootstrap
    inference, permutation testing, and higher-order networks (Higher-Order
    Network, Higher-Order Network Embedding, Hyper-Path Anomaly, Multi-Order
    Generative Model). Includes multi-cluster multi-layer networks (MCML),
    multilevel vector autoregression (VAR), and graphical VAR.
